## ğŸ§® KPI Metrics
| KPI | Description | Purpose |
|-----|-------------|---------|
| ğŸ’° **Total Funded Amount** | Total disbursed loan value | Measures portfolio size |
| âš ï¸ **Default Rate** | Defaults Ã· Total Loans Ã— 100 | Monitors credit risk |
| ğŸ”¢ **Average Interest Rate** | Mean of all issued loan interest rates | Tracks loan pricing |
| ğŸ“‰ **Profit/Loss** | Interest income â€“ charge-offs + recoveries | Assesses portfolio profitability |
| ğŸ“Š **Active Loans** | Total current unpaid loans | Gauges exposure |

